	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=130043><span id= >Takata</span></a><br><span id=notbold>294 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.75]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Greetings all,<br><br>Well after reading all these posts, I was wondering where everyone makes thier plat? As a warrior its very hard to solo things for when you want some extra platinum, I have a couple of ideas and places in mind that I'm willing to share with you all. First of all, the most obvious one is giant killing in RM. Giants can drop between 20 to 40p a kill. Then sometimes they can be very stingy and drop only 2 to 4pp. Or even no pp and just a bunch of gold. Another idea is farming silks, both spider and spiderling silks still sell pretty fast in the bazaar. But farming for silks can be very time consuming. As well as farming for HQ pelts. If anyone has any other neat ideas, hopefully more for the soloing warrior, post your ideas here :)</p>&nbsp;<br>Marshall Takata K'Trazz<br>LVL 65 Darkelf Overlord<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=251453" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=251453</a></td></td></tr>
