	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=212479><span id= >Raznok</span></a><br><span id=notbold>14 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>In Old Sebilis, with a group of 6 (50-56) doing ML style I make 1.5-2k a day usually...if you were to go there with just a cleric (it's pretty much a cakewalk most of the times for my group) you'd probably make out quite well.<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>BriSTleBaNE's DeLIriuM<br>Torv<br>Baron Razok Snowbound - 59 Barb War<br>Yaargh Halfkeg - 50 Dwf Clr<br>Lusis Zy'Tark - 41 DE Necro<br>Lysis Daggerwagger - 24 Wood Elf Rogue<br>Oejig -24 Eru Ench<br><br></td></td></tr>
